title: They are Back!!!... But One
itunes:title: They are Back!!!... But One
description:
Wednesday 1/3- You know the saying "New Year, New Me" so we opened up the phone lines to see hear what our listeners were doing for their New Years Resolutions. Moreover, since Charlamagne is still on vacation while the rest of us are shivering in the cold, we had our listeners call up to give who ever they want for "Donkey of the Day". Also, Angela helped out some listeners during "Ask Yee", but don't let any of that distract you from the fact that it was also Angela Yee's birthday today!!!
